-awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><div class=\"imageframe-align-center\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-8 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"731\" title=\"canada-12\" src=\"http:\/\/site-ssccanada-live-1523224571-vytetvzxegbutqs7mm9.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/canada-12.jpg\" alt class=\"img-responsive wp-image-102\" srcset=\"http:\/\/site-ssccanada-live-1523224571-vytetvzxegbutqs7mm9.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/canada-12-200x292.jpg 200w, http:\/\/site-ssccanada-live-1523224571-vytetvzxegbutqs7mm9.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/canada-12-400x585.jpg 400w, http:\/\/site-ssccanada-live-1523224571-vytetvzxegbutqs7mm9.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/canada-12.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/span><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-22 fusion_builder_column_1_2 1_2 fusion-one-half fusion-column-last\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;width:50%;width:calc(50% - ( ( 4% ) * 0.5 ) );\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-flex-column-wrapper-legacy\"><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-9\"><h3><span style=\"color: #7b197a;\">Guardian application Process:<\/span><\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Parents or legal guardians must sign a \u201cParental Consent to Custodianship\u201d, granting\u00a0<strong>SSC-Canada\u00a0<\/strong>the authority to act as the student&#8217;s custodian. This form will be sent to the student after they have submitted their application. This document must be notarized in your home country and sent to\u00a0<strong>SSC-Canada.<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>\u2028Upon receipt of your notarized Parental Consent and after payment of the necessary fees,\u00a0<strong>SSC-Canada\u00a0<\/strong>will send you a notarized document, signed by the custodian in Canada, declaring that\u00a0<strong>SSC-Canada<\/strong>\u00a0has accepted the role of custodian for you.<\/li>\n<li>\u2028In addition to your Letter of Acceptance from your school, you will take these documents when you apply for your study permit.\u2028\u2028The purpose of this entire process is to satisfy the CIC that adequate arrangements have been made for the care and support for minor children who travel to Canada to study.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><strong><u>Study\u00a0<\/u><u>monitoring\u00a0<\/u><u>human\u00a0<\/u><u>duty\u00a0<\/u><u>and\u00a0<\/u><u>responsibility\u00a0<\/u><u>of any<\/u><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>The Canadian law governing defines the obligations of a custodian to:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Make adequate arrangements for the care and support of the student and<\/li>\n<li>Reside within a reasonable distance of the minor child\u2019s intended residence and school.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Pupils<\/p>\n<p>All primary school students attending the Vancouver School District must live with their parents or adult immediate family members (such as grandparents, aunts, aunts, aunts, aunts, uncles, uncles).\u00a0Student Permit Students must obtain a valid student visa before leaving their place of residence to attend various schools under the Vancouver Board of Education.\u00a0Students must apply for a student visa on their own from the Canadian embassy or consulate in their place of origin.\u00a0For more information, please contact the Canadian Embassy or inquiry<\/p>\n<p>Health and accident insurance<\/p>\n<p>British Columbia requires comprehensive health and accident insurance.\u00a0Every overseas student must have this guarantee while studying in Vancouver.\u00a0Overseas students can receive medical and hospital benefits through the government&#8217;s Medical Service Plan (MSP).<\/p>\n<h3><\/h3>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-clearfix\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-15","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/site-ssccanada-live-1523224571-vytetvzxegbutqs7mm9.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/15","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/site-ssccanada-live-1523224571-vytetvzxegbutqs7mm9.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/site-ssccanada-live-1523224571-vytetvzxegbutqs7mm9.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/site-ssccanada-live-1523224571-vytetvzxegbutqs7mm9.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/site-ssccanada-live-1523224571-vytetvzxegbutqs7mm9.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/site-ssccanada-live-1523224571-vytetvzxegbutqs7mm9.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/15\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/site-ssccanada-live-1523224571-vytetvzxegbutqs7mm9.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}